A. 社区版许可（Community Edition License）  
适用范围 / Scope  
- 软件仅能运行或部署在由 CamThink 生产或授权的硬件设备上。  
- 不得在第三方硬件设备上用于商业化用途（包括但不限于销售、收费服务、OEM/ODM 等）。  
- The software may only be run or deployed on hardware devices manufactured or authorized by CamThink.  
- It must not be used for commercial purposes on non-CamThink hardware (including but not limited to product sales, paid services, OEM/ODM, etc.).

授权条款 / Grant of License  
1. CamThink hereby grants you a worldwide, non-exclusive, non-transferable, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, modify and distribute the Software subject to the above Scope.  
   公司（CamThink）授予您全球、非独占、不可转让、免版税许可，用于使用、复制、修改、分发本软件，前提为上述适用范围。  
2. If you distribute modified or derivative works, you must retain all copyright and license notices and mark your changes accordingly.  
   若您分发修改版本或派生作品，必须保留版权声明、许可证引用及注明您的修改。  
3. The Software is provided “AS IS”. CamThink disclaims all warranties, whether express or implied.  
   本软件按“AS IS／现状”提供，CamThink 不承担任何明示或暗示担保。  
4. The license granted under this section will terminate automatically if you fail to comply with these terms.  
   若您违反本条款，则本许可自动终止。

