B. 商业版许可（Commercial Edition License）  
适用范围 / Scope  
- 软件运行或部署在 非 CamThink 硬件设备上，或用于商业化产品/服务、OEM/ODM、销售等用途。  
- The Software is deployed on non-CamThink hardware, or is used in a commercial product/service, OEM/ODM, or resale context.  
- In these cases, you must enter into a separate Commercial License Agreement with CamThink.  
  在此类情形下，必须与 CamThink 签署 单独商业授权协议。

授权条款 / Grant of License  
1. Upon payment of the applicable license fee and compliance with the agreement, CamThink grants you a worldwide, non-exclusive, non-transferable, perpetual (or term) license to use, reproduce, modify and distribute the Software as defined in your separate license.  
   在您签署商业授权协议并支付适用费用后，CamThink 授予您全球、非独占、不可转让、（永久或限期）使用、复制、修改、分发本软件的权利。  
