   商业授权协议将明确设备范围、再分发权限、闭源或开源要求、支持服务、许可费用等条款。  
3. The Software is provided “AS IS”. To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, CamThink shall not be liable for any indirect, special, consequential or incidental damages arising out of your use of the Software.  
