选择指南 / How to Choose  
- 如果您 **仅在 CamThink 硬件上使用且非商用目的**，请选择 **A. 社区版许可**。  
- If you intend to deploy the software on non-CamThink hardware or for commercial product/service use, please contact <contact-email> for a Commercial License (Section B).  
- 若您对是否属于“商用用途”或“非 CamThink 硬件”存疑，请提前与 CamThink 联系。  
- If you are unsure whether your use constitutes “commercial use” or “non-CamThink hardware”, please contact CamThink in advance.

